==Exporting MIDI files==

To export a [[MIDI file]] in Logic first select the MIDI regions you wish to incorporate into the MIDI file by selecting them in the arrange window.


Then go to '''File/Export/Selection as MIDI file'''



==Importing MIDI files==

To import MIDI file you can simply drag and drop them from the desktop to the arrenge window in Logic. You can also go to '''File/Import''' and select the file.



